Help Type: topic
Topic: troubleshoot

Troubleshooting

No search results:
  Try fewer keywords, remove restrictive `--type` filters, or inspect the archive with:
    wikigraph <archive-uri> index

Missing generated objects:
  Queue the relevant generation task for the chapter:
    wikigraph <chapter-uri> queue add --task reading-graph --accept-cost
    wikigraph <chapter-uri> queue add --task reading-summary --accept-cost

Need machine-readable output:
  Use `--json` or `--jsonl` on object commands.
  `wikigraph config status` is the exception: it prints JSON by default and does not accept `--json`.

URI rejected:
  Do not pass a bare filesystem path to object commands. Convert it first:
    /Users/me/book.sdpub -> wkg:///Users/me/book.sdpub
  If you copied a short URI such as `wkg://entity/Q8018` from output, prepend the archive locator:
    wkg:///Users/me/book.sdpub/entity/Q8018

Help did not appear:
  Append `--help` after the verb you are trying to inspect:
    wikigraph wkg://book.sdpub/chapter list --help
    wikigraph wkg://book.sdpub/entity/Q8018 get --help
